This adapter controls equipment through the Marzhauser TANGO family of controllers. It is tested for Tango-DT with serial interface. Windows is also tested for Tango-PCI and Tango-DT with USB intefrace. To configure Micro-Manager to work with Marzhauser Tango you need to do the following steps:
<table><tr><td>
<tr><td>1.</td><td>Install the TANGO and verify that it works.</td></tr>
<tr><td>2.</td><td>Switch TANGO to Ludl MAC5000 compatible mode.</td></tr>
<tr><td>3.</td><td>Download the MMConfig_Tango.cfg example configuration file.</td></tr>
</table>

